{"tid":1828554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"貼連儂牆送頭不了？而家對家進化緊 我哋係咪仲唔做嘢","createTime":"2020-01-18T03:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T10:43:49.000Z","uid":294614,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"81215092da269eb46c17633ce2689c358541a4b1","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:21:15.000Z","msg":"話說今朝打開手機睇YouTube <br />\n睇睇下彈啲咁嘅嘢俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uayJxu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuayJxu3.png&h=4c668f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家班撚屌已經進化左喺YouTube賣廣告抹黑我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同之前CCTV一樣 <br />\n而對家已經做緊嘢 如果我哋仲停喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點搞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可能會話貼連儂牆會俾人拉<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係大家係唔係唔記得咗有一樣野<br />\n叫做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Airdrop</span></span><br />\n小弟最近已經好少收到手足嘅airdrop文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲懷念以前日日搭車嘅時候都收到AirDrop<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47QseMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47QseMy.jpg&h=f6dc174e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就以為我上面張圖為例<br />\nAirdrop左16個人<br />\n有八個接收左 <br />\n已經有一半成功率<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且只係用你一兩分鐘<br />\n抵屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你而家搭緊車搭緊巴士嘅話 <br />\n希望你可以放低你一兩分鐘嘅時間<br />\n幫下手AirDrop啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你依家搭緊黨鐵<br />\n希望你唔好唔記得佢哋呢幾個月點對香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rK6SqYm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrK6SqYm.jpg&h=92276918&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpmbGwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpmbGwH.jpg&h=34b3b3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我明白有時都係迫於無奈先搭<br />\n所以<br />\n如果你覺得內疚想贖罪嘅話<br />\n唔該你而家由車尾一路AirDrop<br />\n聽日1.19遊行集會去到車頭<br />\n為受傷 被補 被自殺嘅手足做返啲嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfnVoKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfnVoKn.jpg&h=28ad96f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我雖勢弱言輕 但決不缺作無聲</span><br />\n<br />\n希望以後收到你嘅AirDrop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.19聽日見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有普選唯有獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"c973201b19fb7eaf4bac652289974a4e394217c7","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"話雖如此<br />\n但係我唔係叫大家唔好貼連儂牆嘅意思<br />\n只係想提醒返大家唔係剩係得一個方法<br />\n可以兩樣嘢相輔相成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd448652411dc304b847df1de5ca763ad9009ef","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇連登仔幫手推"},{"pid":"c6d826bf5270e89f18fccaaaca9714f664f6c630","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"@連登仔"},{"pid":"d777ef4511c47232dd079282791329d1dd72c04c","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲未瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8babcf4675be3f2c5bd602dfb0e1a3dfe6bfa0","tid":1828554,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6f25b78c6c177b35155aea9db88145da4c4fa69","tid":1828554,"uid":23085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"推 有用"},{"pid":"3c337e7538d4ec4989e65cd54576495c26c3f12c","tid":1828554,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e23c3978d8ed24e4f3114a2c0122ab890457b9d","tid":1828554,"uid":37762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"721唔係黑警最大責任?<br />\n我反而想知狗鐵當時可以做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e03a03be43ac5e15f6a901044351be3386a6785","tid":1828554,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce1bda13b4035ff47c854a5d440dd11167a159a","tid":1828554,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a45bc886b385134378d3e413e3d8d5ba24d0216","tid":1828554,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"964c06505581a0883458cfd6d853748d137ab368","tid":1828554,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:43:57.000Z","msg":"流動連儂+廣告打對家"},{"pid":"f7259ed0a0b9b8ac06eb5b9389cd02e83aa974e5","tid":1828554,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e23c3978d8ed24e4f3114a2c0122ab890457b9d","tid":1828554,"uid":37762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"721唔係黑警最大責任?<br />\n我反而想知狗鐵當時可以做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"乘客上左車閂咗門<br />\n黨鐵開返門俾返鄉黑上車打人？"},{"pid":"a0db32f634fab673ad65c0dc34fbbf75d9d8a09a","tid":1828554,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"唔好再用送頭呢個詞語<br />\n對香港人嚟講無所謂送唔送頭<br />\n不作為嘅後果係全民被清算<br />\n有被捕風險唔會係你唔去行動嘅原因<br />\n牆要照貼 提高警覺 萬事小心"},{"pid":"70a66aa39ba8e794052b98ec03c8a96bc08c245d","tid":1828554,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"咁慘咁 幫你推<br />\n隨街貼嚟啦"},{"pid":"f6427f8ba98a05b0f071193181338a00c6dea22d","tid":1828554,"uid":224298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69a580f33a52204988260416c7ae8d0a6b78b6e3","tid":1828554,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53f4dAb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53f4dAb.gif&h=755d7b56&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}